After taking care of Dollen Megaton turns his attention to Tankor. "It seems
I can't play favorites so I'll have to eliminate you as well." He flies a
little higher into the thinner air, fills his Ice Lung with air and exhales
releasing his saliva as a series of five ice spikes hurtling down on the
vehicon.
